213
00:08:10,380 --> 00:08:12,020
They just wanna know that you're sorry.

214
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:13,140
Do that and you'll be fine.

215
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:13,980
Make sense?

216
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,120
Mm-hmm.

217
