223
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:27,680
I always say bear me.

224
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:30,080
Gets a laugh like a quarter of the time.

225
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,800
So how's, what's her name?

226
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,240
You knew her name.

227
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,080
Who, Karen?

228
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,880
Yeah, she's only one of my oldest friends.

229
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:39,000
How's the apartment hanging?

230
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:39,840
It's fine.

231
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,000
Nice.

232
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:45,580
Check out this sunshine, man.

233
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:46,740
Global warming, right?

234
00:08:47,780 --> 00:08:50,340
Today was supposed to be really cold, I bet.

235
00:08:50,340 --> 00:08:51,740
What about music?

236
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:53,220
You got any music?

237
